[{"question":"What is it and how threatening is it going to be in the next 24 hours?","answer":"It is a long -term event that has to get its act together.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":32,"aSentId":33},{"question":"What was going through my mind when I found out you want to interview me?","answer":"No, no, no.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":86,"aSentId":87},{"question":"I\u0027m sorry, could you say that last part again?","answer":"Let me shorten my questions.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":99,"aSentId":100},{"question":"People are calling me a hero?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":103,"aSentId":104},{"question":"To actually go through it, to see your family home going up in flames, to see the neighborhood where I believe your wife has lived since she was 4 years old, so many families and friends that you know being so badly affected, what does it do to a community?","answer":"It brings a community like ours very much together.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":120,"aSentId":121},{"question":"What is your view of it?","answer":"Well, I think he\u0027s not a hero and I think a lot of people are trying to turn him into that.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":146,"aSentId":147},{"question":"Jeffrey, your reaction?","answer":"Can you imagine -- I mean, here is this 29-year-old high school dropout, well, he scrutinized these documents very carefully and he decided they were not a damage to national security.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":175,"aSentId":176},{"question":"Should the Americans get all uptight about what the Chinese are doing to their computers if it turns out they\u0027re doing the same thing?","answer":"We have a national security agency to do foreign intelligence in other countries.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":194,"aSentId":195},{"question":"But when it\u0027s normal grandpa and grandpa\u0027s phone call on Mother\u0027s Day or Father\u0027s Day?","answer":"OK.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":220,"aSentId":221},{"question":"Why should it be so all encompassing and why aren\u0027t the American people entitled to know about it?","answer":"Well, because of the technology they have, they need this enormous meta data to -- as Jeremy Bash, who is a senior official said - in order to find a needle in a haystack, you need to have the haystack.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":226,"aSentId":227},{"question":"Jeffrey Toobin?","answer":"I think it\u0027s a terrible thought, it\u0027s a terrible idea.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":255,"aSentId":256},{"question":"He was trying quite hard to get to first base, wasn\u0027t he?","answer":"Well, he was trying to get information from journalists to prosecute people who leak.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":264,"aSentId":265},{"question":"Now, why shouldn\u0027t they also face the same potential charges as he has?","answer":"Because the First Amendment specifically refers to the freedom of the press.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":271,"aSentId":272},{"question":"Ben Ferguson, would you jail journalists over this?","answer":"No, I wouldn\u0027t.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":275,"aSentId":276},{"question":"Isn\u0027t that what the founding fathers, Jeffrey, intended the Second Amendment to mean?","answer":"This is an example how much the debate changed in this country.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":322,"aSentId":323},{"question":"Did you fear that she was very seriously hurt?","answer":"I wasn\u0027t afraid of the gunman, obviously, I went running back out there and he was still out there.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":397,"aSentId":398},{"question":"When you saw Jerri again for the first time tonight, I mean, you\u0027ve obviously been through this extraordinary experience together where both of you could have lost your lives quite easily, what was that moment like for you when you -- when you met?","answer":"We gave each other big hugs.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":418,"aSentId":419},{"question":"What is your view given what you\u0027ve been through?","answer":"Well, Piers, I actually grew up down south.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":429,"aSentId":430},{"question":"Debra, say -- you want to say something?","answer":"Debra wants to say one thing --","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":450,"aSentId":451},{"question":"What was your take on what happened in court today?","answer":"Well, it was interesting because not only did he not say a word, but he walked in with his head down and he had his hands cuffed, he had his ankles cuffed as well, but I noticed in looking at the videotape later something very striking.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":478,"aSentId":479},{"question":"Could that play a part in him avoiding the death penalty in this case which may be the only unresolved thing left?","answer":"Well, it remains to be seen if the prosecutor or how much the prosecutor will take into account the feelings of the victims and the relatives.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":492,"aSentId":493},{"question":"Is this likely to succeed as a charge, do you think, if it comes to trial?","answer":"Good evening, Piers, and thanks for having me on.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":506,"aSentId":507},{"question":"What happened?","answer":"It was a happy time for me.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":541,"aSentId":542},{"question":"What did you feel?","answer":"I first got the phone call, and I was -- I didn\u0027t believe -- not that I didn\u0027t believe it.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":552,"aSentId":553},{"question":"How did you do it?","answer":"Well, first I -- 10 years later I tried to get information, and when I got the nerve to go to the precinct.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":579,"aSentId":580},{"question":"And what was the breakthrough moment?","answer":"2008, I find these Background Checks.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":600,"aSentId":601},{"question":"That\u0027s online service which checks people\u0027s names, right?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":605,"aSentId":606},{"question":"And eventually you began to piece it all together and then you went to the police again?","answer":"No, I just put that away.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":618,"aSentId":619},{"question":"So what was the moment you went to the police?","answer":"November of 2012.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":623,"aSentId":624},{"question":"And how quickly was it the police found the guy?","answer":"Very quickly.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":636,"aSentId":637},{"question":"But all from the information you gave them?","answer":"I guess.","docId":"130612pmt","qSentId":640,"aSentId":641}]